data.description: Potential Homeowners and Investors, get ready to be impressed! This stunning corner unit located in the heart of Yeadon, Pennsylvania is coming soon for purchase. Boasting a spacious front yard with a cozy porch, you'll have plenty of room to relax and entertain guests. The separate basement entrance adds even more potential to this already amazing property. With three bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this unit offers plenty of space for a growing family or to use as a rental property. Yeadon, Pennsylvania is a great neighborhood for many reasons! Here are a few reasons why it might be a great place for you to move to; affordability, location, sense of community, abundance of amenities, and safety. Overall, Yeadon, Pennsylvania offers a great combination of affordability, convenience, community, and safety, making it a great place to call home. All this for just $180,000 - this is a deal you don't want to miss! Book a viewing soon and take the first step towards making this investment yours.
